{"tid":1369211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗、屯門、天水圍休息站","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:35:51.000Z","uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"327e00a689140bf7286391722631245b7308f360","tid":1369211,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"利申：非元朗友、P牌絲打、一向為公義發聲的教友<br />\n只希望各位戰友多一個地方休息<br />\n有冷氣、飲用水、急救用品、廁所<br />\n<br />\n【元朗 屯門 天水圍 聖堂 祈禱站 休息站】<br />\n【2019.7.27週六開放情況】<br />\n<br />\n＝＝聖伯多祿聖保祿堂（元朗）<br />\n27/7&mdash;&mdash;祈禱和反思日<br />\n上午8時：明供朝拜聖體（小聖堂）<br />\n下午3時： 慈悲時刻（大聖堂）<br />\n下午5時：彌撒（大聖堂 &ndash; 英語）<br />\n晚上6時30 分：彌撒（大聖堂 &ndash; 粵語）<br />\n由晚上8 時開始：祈禱和反思時間（大聖堂）<br />\n歡迎大家隨時來臨一起參與祈禱。<br />\n地址：新界元朗青山公路201號屏山段<br />\n電話：24760887<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SSPETERANDPAUL.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSSPETERANDPAUL.HK&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=2a3f88d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SSPETERANDPAUL.HK</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝屯門贖世主堂<br />\n27/7下午3時起明供聖體，為香港社會祈禱。<br />\n同時，亦會開放地方給有需要人士作休息之用。<br />\n地址：屯門鄉事會路二號<br />\n電話：2459 6510<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/holyredeemerchurchhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fholyredeemerchurchhk&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=deca099a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/holyredeemerchurchhk</a><br />\n<br />\n＝天水圍聖葉理諾堂<br />\n27/7通宵開放至翌日<br />\n作祈禱/輔導/護理/休息之用<br />\n地址：天水圍天美街6號<br />\n電話：2448 8332<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stjeromeschurch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstjeromeschurch&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e0a4e5ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stjeromeschurch</a>"},{"pid":"5280ea80f11f293d617a613915ba043ce8a5c32b","tid":1369211,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"88000278f581ab2066e7cc9420b637ee121bd29a","tid":1369211,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqOzi.png&h=002dc61c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n更新左加入更多地標, 遊行路線, 有意見隨時回答, 謝"},{"pid":"f78ebb6ecbd091eca9cbd9a77285fbf83371ec8c","tid":1369211,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88000278f581ab2066e7cc9420b637ee121bd29a","tid":1369211,"uid":57328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqOzi.png&h=002dc61c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n更新左加入更多地標, 遊行路線, 有意見隨時回答, 謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"好快手！大家加油！"}]}